item.title: Clinical Decision Support System for COVID-19 patients management
item.description: Everybody has head about COVID The first case of COVID-19 was detected in Wuhan, China, on December 31st, 2019. Soon after, the WHO has characterized this viral disease as a global pandemic. Many governments have imposed a lockdown to protect the NHS from being overwhelmed and limit the spread of the disease. Since then, the COVID-19 has seriously impacted businesses and the economy. It also has been had serious implications for people’s livelihoods and health.
